# Conway's Game of Life

## What is life-tk?

life-tk if python implementation of [Conway's Game of Life](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conway%27s_Game_of_Life) based on [tkinter](https://docs.python.org/3/library/tkinter.html) GUI.

## How does life-tk work?

Requirments: need to be installed python3 and tk packeages. Enter in terminal emulator:

    python life-tk

## What is life-tk goal?

life-tk is a tutorial project to implement Conway's Game of Life based on the tkinter package in OOP style.
